ns0:doc.ns2:hint: This is full WADL including extended resources. To get simplified WADL with users resources only do not use the query parameter detail. Link: https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/api/dissemination/sdmx/2.1/sdmx-rest.wadl

ns0:grammars.ns0:doc: The SDMXMessage.xsd is used to import all SDMXML types so as to be referenced in the WADL.The SDMXRestTypes.xsd defines various types used by the WADL's parameters e.g. key pattern, latest and all values.
